<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-08-10T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-08-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="1266" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1266">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72111/2710</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Acting Secretary of the Navy</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Burson</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the</hi>
                            <gloss type="to">
                                <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State</hi>
                            </gloss>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-08-10">
                                    <hi rend="italic">August 10, 1915</hi>.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to forward herewith, for
                            your information, a copy of a cablegram, received from the commandant of
                            the naval station, Guam, relative to the establishment of a censorship
                            over the cables to that place.</p>
                        <p>Sincerely yours,</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">W. S. Burson</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                        <frus:attachment>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Enclosure—Telegram—Paraphrase]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Commandant of the Naval Station at Guam</hi>
                                    (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Maxwell</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the Secretary of the
                                    Navy</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_DJ1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Daniels</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Guam</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-08-10">
                                        <hi rend="italic">August 10, 1915</hi>.</date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>Have established censorship over the cable. The company demurred over
                                censorship but commandant has taken charge of office.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Maxwell</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </frus:attachment>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>